1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:50,900 --> 00:00:52,100
Lieutenant Cheng,

4
00:00:54,420 --> 00:00:55,940
do you think these flowers look nice?

5
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:07,140
They do.

6
00:01:08,220 --> 00:01:09,580
They're especially beautiful.

7
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:13,660
Lieutenant Cheng.

8
00:01:25,060 --> 00:01:26,220
Lieutenant Cheng.

9
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:27,900
Let go of me!

10
00:01:29,820 --> 00:01:31,300
Let go!

11
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:40,380
Let go!

12
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:51,500
I heard the guns have arrived.

13
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:53,420
- Tell them to be extra careful.
- Alright.

14
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:56,900
Why is one of your buttons missing?

15
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:00,339
Are you blind or what?

16
00:03:00,340 --> 00:03:01,620
Sorry.

17
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:03,500
It's fine. Go get back to work.

18
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:08,640
It's just a pair of shoes.

19
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:10,700
Since when did you become
so careful with your things?

20
00:03:10,700 --> 00:03:11,219
Well,

21
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:13,100
you gave them to me.

22
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:14,780
Of course I'd treasure them.

23
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:17,620
It's nothing.
I can always buy you another pair.

24
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:19,900
You're the Commander now.

25
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,880
I have to pay attention
to these things too.

26
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,380
Can't let you lose face because of me.

27
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:26,380
What are you talking about?

28
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:28,100
No matter who I am,

29
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:30,100
you'll always be my best brother.

30
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:30,780
Mm.

31
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:32,220
Best brother.

32
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:34,420
I'm leaving.

33
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:48,940
(Divorce Agreement)

34
00:03:58,180 --> 00:03:59,380
A divorce agreement?

35
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:01,060
How...

36
00:04:01,580 --> 00:04:03,140
How was everything fine yesterday?

37
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:14,140
Xinran.

38
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:16,220
Xinran.

39
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,380
Where did she go
so early in the morning?

40
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:21,020
She didn't even tidy up the room.

41
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:44,220
Zhuang Yunqiu.

42
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:45,460
Xue Wan.

43
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:49,279
These past two days,
the Commander and I have been discussing

44
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,460
what gift to buy for you.

45
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:52,460
We were planning
to go apologize in person.

46
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:53,700
Zhuang Yunqiu,

47
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:55,420
drop the act.

48
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:57,260
Where did you hide Gu Nianchi?

49
00:04:57,460 --> 00:04:58,580
Give him back to me.

50
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:00,340
Gu Nianchi?

51
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:02,260
What are you talking about?

52
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:04,299
You locked him up

53
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,940
and turned him into that state.

54
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,700
You vicious woman.

55
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,700
Why would you do this to my husband?

56
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:11,700
So you knew I locked him up.

57
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:15,100
You're the one who let him go?

58
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:16,060
That's right.

59
00:05:16,220 --> 00:05:17,420
I saved him.

60
00:05:17,620 --> 00:05:18,579
But now he's gone.

61
00:05:18,580 --> 00:05:20,200
I've searched everywhere
and still can't find him.

62
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:22,100
You must've locked him up again.

63
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:23,780
Zhuang Yunqiu,

64
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,420
he doesn't love you.

65
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:26,859
The one he loves is me.

66
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:28,300
And I love him too.

67
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:30,260
Stop wasting your efforts.

68
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:32,020
He told you he loves you?

69
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:33,300
That's right.

70
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,340
We're already husband and wife,

71
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:37,020
and we've already
consummated the marriage.

72
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:40,540
I know.

73
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,740
Back then,
because I didn't want to marry him,

74
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:44,540
I agreed to let you marry him instead.

75
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,219
But at the time, I didn't know

76
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:48,140
Gu Nianchi was the one
fate had chosen for me.

77
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:49,940
Only now do I realize that I love him.

78
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:53,620
In this Commander's Residence,

79
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:55,180
it's all about fame and fortune.

80
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:58,540
As long as you're willing
to leave the Commander,

81
00:05:58,740 --> 00:06:01,260
the Xue family can give you
anything you want.

82
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:02,940
Xue Wan,

83
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:05,019
I'm truly sorry about this matter.

84
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:06,620
I should've told you sooner.

85
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,700
Gu Nianchi is already dead.

86
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:11,900
The current Commander isn't Gu Nianchi,

87
00:06:12,220 --> 00:06:14,940
but his twin brother, Lu Shaoyuan.

88
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:17,340
Zhuang Yunqiu,

89
00:06:17,980 --> 00:06:19,139
you'll really make up

90
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:21,100
any lie now just to fool me.

91
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:23,179
I know it's hard for you
to accept right away,

92
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:24,700
but this is the truth.

93
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:26,180
If you think about it carefully,

94
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:29,179
the former Commander had
a terrible reputation in Yancheng.

95
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:30,259
He oppressed the people.

96
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:32,419
But the current Commander
is completely different.

97
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:32,779
So...

98
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:33,820
So what?

99
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:36,429
You were the one saying before
that he committed every evil imaginable.

100
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:39,219
And now you're the one saying
he serves the city and its people.

101
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:41,379
Which of your words are true,
and which are lies?

102
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:43,580
Xue Wan, I'm not lying to you.

103
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:45,540
They're two different people.

104
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:46,580
Fine.

105
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,200
You said he's dead.

106
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:50,600
If he's alive, I want to see the person.
If he's dead, I want to see the body.

107
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:52,300
Take me to his corpse.

108
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:53,139
I...

109
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:54,660
Can't answer that, can you?

110
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:57,900
Looks to me like you just want to keep
the title of Commander's wife for yourself

111
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:59,540
and don't want to give
it back to me, right?

112
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:01,260
Xue Wan,

113
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,980
I never thought
you'd distrust me this much.

114
00:07:04,220 --> 00:07:05,940
But everything I said is true.

115
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:08,660
If that's the case,

116
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:10,820
then I'll go ask Xinran.

117
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:13,740
You say there are two Commanders.

118
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:15,579
Even if you won't tell me,

119
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:16,980
someone else eventually will.

120
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:20,100
This matter
absolutely cannot be made public.

121
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:21,620
It's a secret.

122
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:24,700
Fine.

123
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:27,500
Even if what you said is true,

124
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:30,339
I don't care which Commander it is now.

125
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:32,140
That position was originally mine.

126
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:33,900
I want it back.

127
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:36,740
Xue Wan,

128
00:07:37,340 --> 00:07:39,140
I'm truly sorry about this.

129
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:40,820
But what I want to say is,

130
00:07:41,540 --> 00:07:43,820
I've never wanted
to be the Commander's wife.

131
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:45,900
I only want to be his wife.

132
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:48,300
You can make me do anything,

133
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:50,340
but I have to stay by his side.

134
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,620
He's the most
important person in my life.

135
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:53,940
No matter what,

136
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:55,940
I will never leave him.

137
00:07:57,020 --> 00:07:59,260
Zhuang Yunqiu, you're shameless.

138
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:01,620
I know you won't believe
anything I say anymore.

139
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:03,580
But this is the truth.

140
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:05,460
Since that's the case,

141
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:07,660
take out your anger however you want.

142
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:09,740
I won't fight back.

143
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:13,180
Don't think I wouldn't dare hit you.

144
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:18,540
Nianchi.

145
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:21,180
Shaoyuan.

146
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:23,780
She may have agreed to it,

147
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:25,860
but she's my woman.

148
00:08:26,540 --> 00:08:27,580
And I won't allow it.

149
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:31,340
Miss Xue, be careful.

150
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:39,780
Nianchi.

151
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:42,820
Why were you
so affectionate toward me before,

152
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,940
but treating me like this now?

153
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:45,899
Did you forget

154
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:47,699
how she locked you up before?

155
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,579
I'm telling you...

156
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:49,820
Forget it. Stop talking.

157
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:51,700
Xue Wan,

158
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:53,259
this is all my fault.

159
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:55,060
I'll keep begging for your forgiveness

160
00:08:55,180 --> 00:08:56,980
until the day you truly forgive me.

161
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,460
Xue Wan,

162
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:01,580
whatever grievance you have,
take it out on me.

163
00:09:07,020 --> 00:09:08,260
Please,

164
00:09:08,900 --> 00:09:10,500
don't make things difficult
for her anymore.

165
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:13,300
Nianchi.

166
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:20,790
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

167
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:27,420
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

168
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:31,500
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

169
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:34,850
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

170
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:40,140
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

171
00:09:41,260 --> 00:09:46,450
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

172
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:53,110
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

173
00:09:53,650 --> 00:09:57,030
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

174
00:09:57,280 --> 00:10:00,229
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

175
00:10:00,230 --> 00:10:05,369
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

176
00:10:05,370 --> 00:10:09,689
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

177
00:10:09,690 --> 00:10:12,269
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

178
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:14,549
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

179
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:18,099
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

180
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:22,629
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

181
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:25,160
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

182
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:27,249
♪Still I walk into♪

183
00:10:27,250 --> 00:10:30,849
♪The trap you set without regret♪

184
00:10:30,850 --> 00:10:34,899
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

185
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:37,479
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

186
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,639
♪A stand in can never cross♪

187
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:43,079
♪The shortest distance between us♪

188
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:48,050
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

189
00:10:48,210 --> 00:10:52,880
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

190
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:57,229
♪A substitute♪

191
00:10:57,230 --> 00:11:02,230
♪Needs no reason♪

